verses.roman:
svarūpa gosāñi, dāmodara, jagadānanda
vaiṣṇavere pariveśe tina jane-ānanda

synonyms: svarūpa gosāñi—Svarūpa Gosāñi; dāmodara—Dāmodara; jagadānanda—Jagadānanda; vaiṣṇavere pariveśe—distributed to the Vaiṣṇavas; tina jane—the three persons; ānanda—very jubilant.
translation: Then Svarūpa Dāmodara Gosvāmī, Dāmodara Paṇḍita and Jagadānanda all began to distribute prasāda to the devotees with great pleasure.
